1 A BILL for an Act to create and enact a new section to chapter 24-01 of the North Dakota
2 Century Code, relating to designating state highway 200 as the North Dakota fallen peace
3 officers memorial highway; and to provide a continuing appropriation.
4 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATIVE ASSEMBLY OF NORTH DAKOTA:
5 SECTION 1. A new section to chapter 24-01 of the North Dakota Century Code is created
6 and enacted as follows:
7 North Dakota fallen peace officers memorial highway - State highway 200 -
8 Continuing appropriation.
9 1. The department shall designate state highway 200 from the Minnesota border to the
10 Montana border as the North Dakota fallen peace officers memorial highway and shall
11 place signs along the highway designating that name.
12 2. The department shall consult with the family and associates of North Dakota peace
13 officers and law enforcement officers, and handlers and owners of canine officers ,
14 killed in the line of duty, to designate up to one mile of state highway 200 to
15 memorialize an individual peace officer, law enforcement officer, or canine officer.
16 3. The department may accept any appropriate signs or funds donated to the department
17 for the placement of signs. Any donated funds are appropriated to the department on a
18 continuing basis for the purpose of providing signs designating state highway 200 as
19 the North Dakota fallen peace officers memorial highway.
